<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Internship Information Portal</title>
  <style>
    /* General Reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #e3f2fd, #fce4ec);
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Hero Section */
    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #004080, #0066cc);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    /* Navigation */
    nav {
      background: #0066cc;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 15px;
    }

    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #ffeb3b;
    }

    /* Container */
    .container {
      padding: 40px;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    /* Cards */
    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 30px;
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .card h2 {
      color: #004080;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .card ul {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .card ul li {
      background: #f1f8ff;
      margin: 8px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }

    .card ul li:hover {
      background: #bbdefb;
    }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background: #004080;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }

    /* Animations */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {opacity: 0;}
      to {opacity: 1;}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1> Internship Information Portal </h1>
    <p>Discover, Apply, and Kickstart Your Career Journey</p>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">Internships</a>
    <a href="#">Apply</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="card">
      <h2>About the Portal</h2>
      <p>Welcome to the Internship Information Portal! Here you’ll find curated opportunities across industries, designed to help students gain real-world experience and build their careers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2>🔥 Featured Internships</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Software Development Internship – 3 months</li>
        <li>Marketing & Social Media Internship – 2 months</li>
        <li>Data Analysis Internship – 6 months</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <h2> How to Apply</h2>
      <p>Navigate to the "Apply" section, complete the online form, and upload your resume. Our team will review your application and connect you with the right opportunities.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Internship Portal | Designed to Impress</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
